.\" -*- nroff -*- 
.TH ARCDECISION 1 "@DATE@" "NorduGrid ARC @VERSION@" "NorduGrid Users Manual"

.SH NAME

arcdecision \- ARC client to PDP service

.SH DESCRIPTION

The
.B arcdecision
command is a prototype client which is used for sending a policy decision request to a pdp service.

.SH SYNOPSIS

.B arcdecision [options] [filename ...]

./arcdecision -c pdp_client.xml -d DEBUG -s https://127.0.0.1:60001 -r request.xml

.SH OPTIONS

.IP "\fB-c\fR [-]\fIconfigurefile\fR, \fB-conf\fR [-]\fIconfigurefile\fR"
specify the configuration file of pdp client
.IP "\fB-s\fR [-]\fIserviceurl\fR, \fB-service\fR [-]\fIserviceurl\fR"
specify the url to pdp service
.IP "\fB-r\fR [-]\frequestfile\fR, \fB-request\fR [-]\fIrequestfile\fR"
specify the request file that includes the formatted request (arc or xacml format)
.IP "\fB-p\fR [-]\fIsamlprofile\fR, \fB-saml\fR [-]\fIsamlprofile\fR"
specify the usage of the SAML2.0 profile of XACML
.IP "\fB-d\fR \fIdebuglevel\fR, \fB-debug\fR \fIdebuglevel\fR"
FATAL, ERROR, WARNING, INFO, VERBOSE or DEBUG
.IP "\fB-v\fR, \fB-version\fR"
print version information
.IP "\fB-?\fR, \fB-help\fR"
print help
.LP

.SH EXTENDED DESCRIPTION

The
.B arcdecision
command is a prototype client which is used for sending a policy decision request to a pdp service.

.IR Examples :
.IP "\fBarcdecision -c pdp_client.xml -d DEBUG -s https://127.0.0.1:60001 -r request.xml\fR ..."
send the request to https://127.0.0.1:60001
.LP

.SH FILES

.TP
.B .arc/config.xml
Some options can be given default values by specifying them in the
ARC configuration file.

